lead_paragraph: Argentina's Jaguares notched up their second win in Super Rugby and first at home with a 11-try romp for a 73-27 win over South Africa's Kings at Velez Sarsfield on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Jaguares Claim First Home Win With 11-Try Romp
